import React from 'react'
import Imgslider from './ImgSlider'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom";
import Categoryshow from './Categoryshow'
import Login from './Login';

const MainPage = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Routes>
    <Route path="/women" element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="/women" element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="/men" element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="/kids" element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="/perfume" element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="/login" element={ <Login/> } />
    <Route path="/contact" element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    <Route path="/signup" element={ <Categoryshow/> } />
    </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
     <Imgslider/> 
    </>
  )
}

export default MainPage
